These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, thriller, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, funk, trance, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, german, indian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, boat, car
1. the german is the fan of gospel##1
2. the indian is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the german is the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the australian##1
6. the person driving the boat is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | scientific   | disaster  | thriller  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | gospel    | house      | trance    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | german | indian | australian |
| Transport     | car  | airplane       | quad-bike    | boat     |

