.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, camping, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, epic, disaster, mystery
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, surfing, baseball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person watching mystery movies and the owner of the pony##2
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | dancing    | camping  | fishing    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | epic  | mystery  | disaster |
| Pet           | pony      | hamster       | fish      | chinchilla       |
| Sport         | surfing    | tennis | baseball | biathlon |

