.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, kale, pineapple, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, cooking, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic, designer, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, train, ship
1. the designer is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person eating carrot is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person eating pineapple and the mechanic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | kale | pineapple     | carrot   | avocado     |
| Hobby       | chess   | filmmaking   | cooking | dancing |
| Job         | dancer   | designer | entrepreneur       | mechanic    |
| Transport   | train    | car | bus  | ship    |

