.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, security-guard, photographer, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, spy, thriller
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, cat, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, biathlon, cricket
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is the software-developer##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the dog##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the photographer##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the security-guard is between the owner of the mouse and the scientist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | software-developer  | scientist | security-guard     | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | documentary  | spy | western       |
| Pet           | dog       | fish    | cat      | mouse           |
| Sport         | basketball | surfing   | cricket   | biathlon         |

