 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 3. the musician is the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the musician is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the videographer is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 8. the doctor is the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching time-travel movies##2
10. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | strawberry         | kiwi         | tomato     | spinach      |
| Job           | musician | videographer | teacher    | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel      | sports       | animation    | spy       |
