6. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the designer##1
8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
9. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
