 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the german is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the brazilian is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
