3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the trike and the person watching sports movies##2
6. the person drinking milk is the person watching romance movies##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
