The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, architect, doctor, bartender
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, blues, funk, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, surfing, sailing
 1. the person eating pomegranate is the doctor##1
 2. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the doctor is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 5. the fan of salsa is the person eating peas##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 7. the architect is on the left of the doctor##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 9. the firefighter is between the bartender and the person who's sport is golf##2
10. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | orange        | strawberry    | peas | pomegranate   |
| Job           | bartender | firefighter | architect   | doctor |
| Music-Genre   | funk         | jazz       | salsa      | blues     |
