There 4 different types of food: strawberry, cranberry, eggplant, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, camping, gardening, singing
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, hamster, fish
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating eggplant##2
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating eggplant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | water    | 7up    | soy-milk      | cola |
| Food       | strawberry        | asparagus       | eggplant       | cranberry     |
| Hobby      | gardening | card-games | singing | camping        |
| Pet        | cat       | fish     | hamster         | rabbit           |

