 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating lime##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | plum  | lime | grapes     | watermelon     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse | snake     | rabbit |
| Sport       | basketball  | volleyball   | climbing | badminton    |
| Transport   | trike   | taxi   | quad-bike  | bike        |

